<cell id="cell-0"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type># Lab 3.6 — Hybrid + rerank
Dense (embed-english-v3.0) + BM25 (rank_bm25) + RRF + rerank.
Two reranker options: bge-reranker-v2-m3 (free, local, CPU-ok)
and Cohere rerank-v3.5 (paid, hosted).
Reuses 03-naive-rag corpus + eval questions.
Cost: ~$0.10 (Cohere path); ~$0.00 (bge path, local).</cell id="cell-0">
